* build uplcd

* copy uplcd into /usr/local/bin
* copy uplcr into /usr/local/bin

* add /bin/sh to TCC's Full Disk Access List (if applicable on your system)

* copy local.lcars.uplcd.plist in ~/Library/LaunchAgents
* load the LaunchAgent

* add original DMG basename to dotfile .uplc_rename in the root of the DMG volume
* alternatively: use "testimage_renamed.dmg" in this repository
